BUG-002

Module:
Registration

Environment:
Application: OWASP Juice Shop
Browser: Google Chrome
Operating System: Windows 10/11

Description:
The Security Question dropdown on the Registration page does not display any options when clicked, preventing users from selecting a security question during account registration.

Preconditions:
User has to open the Registration page.
Registration form is loaded successfully.

Steps to Reproduce:
Open the OWASP Juice Shop application.
Click Not yet a customer? to open the Registration page.
Fill in the required registration fields.
Click the Security Question dropdown.
Observe the behavior.

Expected Result:
The Security Question dropdown should expand and display the available security questions for selection.

Actual Result:
The Security Question dropdown does not open, and no options are displayed.

Severity:
High

Priority:
High
